<font STYLE="" SIZE="3"><b STYLE="">二、ArchLinux下编译osmocomBB</b></font><br STYLE=""/>
<font STYLE="" COLOR="DarkSlateGray">(网上其他linux编译的教程很多，如果不是用的Arch可以跳过这个部分，参考其他教程完成osmocomBB编译)</font><br STYLE=""/>
<br STYLE=""/>
0.&nbsp;首先将texinfo替换成4.13a，源里面texinfo5会导致gcc的文档无法编译<br STYLE=""/>

&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE="margin: 5px 20px 20px;">

&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE="font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: 宋体, verdana, geneva, lucida, 'lucida grande', arial, helvetica, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 2px;">代码:</div>


&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<pre STYLE="margin: 0px; background-color: rgb(222, 223, 223); padding: 6px; border: 1px inset; width: 700px; text-align: left; overflow: auto;" DIR="ltr">cd&nbsp;~
svn&nbsp;checkout&nbsp;--depth=empty&nbsp;svn://svn.archlinux.org/packages&nbsp;arch_packages
cd&nbsp;arch_packages
svn&nbsp;update&nbsp;texinfo&nbsp;-r176043
cd&nbsp;texinfo/repos/core-i686
makepkg
</pre>

&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;</div>安装编译好的texinfo-4.13a：<br STYLE=""/>

&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE="margin: 5px 20px 20px;">

&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE="font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: 宋体, verdana, geneva, lucida, 'lucida grande', arial, helvetica, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 2px;">代码:</div>


&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<pre STYLE="margin: 0px; background-color: rgb(222, 223, 223); padding: 6px; border: 1px inset; width: 700px; text-align: left; overflow: auto;" DIR="ltr">sudo&nbsp;pacman&nbsp;-U&nbsp;texinfo-4.13a-7-i686.pkg.tar.xz
</pre>

&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;</div><br STYLE=""/>
<b STYLE="">1.&nbsp;安装libosmocore：</b><a STYLE="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;" TARGET="_blank" HREF="http://bb.osmocom.org/trac/wiki/libosmocore">http://bb.osmocom.org/trac/wiki/libosmocore</a><br STYLE=""/>

&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE="margin: 5px 20px 20px;">

&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE="font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: 宋体, verdana, geneva, lucida, 'lucida grande', arial, helvetica, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 2px;">代码:</div>


&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<pre STYLE="margin: 0px; background-color: rgb(222, 223, 223); padding: 6px; border: 1px inset; width: 700px; text-align: left; overflow: auto;" DIR="ltr">cd&nbsp;~
git&nbsp;clone&nbsp;git://git.osmocom.org/libosmocore.git
cd&nbsp;libosmocore/
#&nbsp;autoreconf&nbsp;-i&nbsp;<font STYLE="" COLOR="Red">(not&nbsp;working)</font>
</pre>

&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;</div><b STYLE="">Arch下autoreconf怎么都过不了，直接无视之继续编译，后面再修复libosmocore.so.4找不到的问题</b><br STYLE=""/>
<br STYLE=""/>

&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE="margin: 5px 20px 20px;">

&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<div STYLE="font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: 宋体, verdana, geneva, lucida, 'lucida grande', arial, helvetica, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 2px;">代码:</div>


&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;<pre STYLE="margin: 0px; background-color: rgb(222, 223, 223); padding: 6px; border: 1px inset; width: 700px; text-align: left; overflow: auto;" DIR="ltr">./configure
make
sudo&nbsp;make&nbsp;install
</pre>

