sudo&nbsp;minicom&nbsp;-D&nbsp;/dev/ttyUSB0&nbsp;-b&nbsp;115385&nbsp;-s
</pre>

&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;</div>在对话框中选择&quot;Serial&nbsp;port&nbsp;setup&quot;，按F键关闭&quot;Hardware&nbsp;Flow&nbsp;Control&quot;，最终配置如图所示：<br STYLE=""/>
