</pre>

&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;&Tab;</div>像刚才一样关掉&quot;Hardware&nbsp;Flow&nbsp;Control&quot;进入，将C118关机并短按电源键，连接正常的话会显示下面的内容先显示ftmtool，接着大约1秒后输出error，看到这个说明连接无误。<br STYLE=""/>
<img src="../_resources/48e62025b9ad78f5143bf390a29555a6.png"  border="0" hash="48e62025b9ad78f5143bf390a29555a6" style="margin: 2px; cursor: pointer;" height="178" alt="" width="346" type="image/png" /></en-media><br STYLE=""/>
