<br STYLE=""/>
为了加深对SMS传输的理解，我写了个Python脚本来重组短信的PDU。<br STYLE=""/>
下面部分需要些GSM网络相关的知识，推荐&nbsp;<a STYLE="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;" TARGET="_blank" HREF="http://web.it.kth.se/~johanmon/attic/2g1723/lectures.html"><font STYLE="" COLOR="blue">GSM&nbsp;network&nbsp;and&nbsp;services&nbsp;2G1723&nbsp;2006</font></a>&nbsp;<br STYLE=""/>
<a STYLE="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;" TARGET="_blank" REL="nofollow"><img src="../_resources/e7701054181a45a43dd70a2f37e8794c.png"  border="0" hash="e7701054181a45a43dd70a2f37e8794c" style="margin: 2px;" height="346" alt="点击图片以查看大图

