          <a STYLE="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;" REL="nofollow"><img src="../_resources/2b68b60f00426e1fd146ccd5507a5f52.gif"  border="0" hash="2b68b60f00426e1fd146ccd5507a5f52" style="vertical-align: middle;" height="12" alt="查看帖子" width="12" title="查看帖子" type="image/gif" /></en-media></a> </div>
